{"/service/ndnp/mimtptc/batch_mimtptc_bath_ver01/data/sn92063852/00279551321/1958042601/0444.xml":{"full_text":"God's Ovist Science Universal Messiah Wotid Healing\n\u201cH* SS \u00a3:.**'T\nPHESEIVT S\u00abw\u00ab*\u00aer TANARUS\u00bb Mw**\u201c* immmhih accohdimo to cmwtiii\nMOT TO KlftAvC UW*f, 0* DITTAOT MtA f IAMAMIMT, COmiOHT.O. .STA.USMO .OTOKMC. THAT WTO.\nA Mv Cmkrt P*o*f. *m (A Orri\u00df-JA\nEISENHOWER ACCUSES CRITICS OF\n'NONSENSE' ON DEFENSE PROGRAM\nHE ASSAILS CHARGES BY VINSON\nNO BLANK CHECK, NO PRUSSIAN STAFF\nBy Robar* J. Donovan\n(N.Y. Tribunt, 4/18)\nby Andrew F. Fruebauf, CS.\nModern Christian Science Cruaadar\nMajor Prophet of \u201cour Father-Mother Cod, all\nharmonious\u201d (p. 16, Science and Health with Key to\nthe Scripture* by Mary Baker Eddy) with a world\n\u25a0eua|e and mission, who will\u2014by the grace of God\n_do a Fruehauf-Martin Luther job hs thii age! 11\nAnd how! Science Sc Health, our textbook, is God\u2019s\nLiberator Os The Bible.\nA HIGHER AND TRUER REPRESENTATIVE OF\nGOD THAN THE POPE AT ROME! AND THE\nWRITER IS HIS FRIEND! AND OF HIS PEOPLE,\nTOO I\nJesus \u201cloved righteousness and hated iniquity\u201d!\nThe \u201clukewarm* live in a \u201cfooPs paradise.\u201d!\n\nWASHINGTON, Apr. 17.\u2014PRESIDENT EISENHOWER,\nVIGOROUSLY DEFENDING HIS MILITARY REORGANI\nZATION PLAN, ACCUSED HIS CRITICS TODAY OF\n\u201cNONSENSE\" AND \u201cMISREPRESENTATION\" AND DE\nMANDED AN END TO \u201cUNWORTHY\" AND \u201cCOSTLY\"\nINTER-SERVICE RIVALRIES.\nTHE PRESIDENT'S CHARGE OF \u201cNONSENSE\" AND\n\u201cFAR-FETCHED REASONING\" WAS AIMED PRIMARILY\nAT REP. CARL VINSON, D., GA., CHAIRMAN OF THE\nHOUSE ARMED SERVICES COMMITTEE. WITHOUT MEN\nTIONING HIM BY NAME MR. EISENHOWER NEVERTHE\nLESS ASSAILED THE STATEMENTS HE HAD MADE\nYESTERDAY THAT THE PLAN THREATENED THE\nCONSTITUTIONAL AUTHORITY OF CONGRESS AND\nMIGHT PRODUCE A \u201cPRESSIAN-TYPE\" HIGH COM\nMAND.\n(Sec ACCUSES CRITICS, Page 11)\nA FIGHT TO THE FINISH\n(N. Y. Tribune Editorial, 4/18)\nPresident Eisenhower clearly is determined to fight his\nbattle for modern defense through to final victory. He is\ntaking his case to the people, as he promised. His first major\nspeech of the crusade went on the TV and radio networks.\nIt was a fighting speech, determined and resolute. It\nwas delivered in the unswerving mood of the supreme com\nmander of old.\nHe was dealing with a subject he knows inside and out,\nhas lived with, as he made clear, since 1911.\nHe charged head-on at the mine-fields and smokescreens\nbeing laid by Georgia's Carl Vinson and other champions\nof MULE-TEAM DEFENSE IN A SATELLITE AGE. To Vin\nson's windy cries of \u201cPrussian general staff man on\nhorseback,\" the President tossed this devastating aside:\n\u201cIt's a habit of ours to set up straw men which we take great\npleasure in beating down. But in this case it seems to me\nthat the men are not made of good, honest straw, even.\nThey scarcely deserve the name of chaff.\"\n(See FIGHT TO FINISH, Page 11)\nDEVIL ROBS DETROIT OF 30 to 50 YEARS\nWISDOM AND SERVICE OF TWO OF ITS\nHUMANITARIAN AND INDUSTRIAL 'GIANTS'-\nTHINKING STARVATIONS OF IMPERATIVE\nCHRIST SUPER SCIENCE UNIVERSAL MESSIAH\nMR. JOHN S. COLEMAN, 60, PROTESTANT, S*. Paul',\nEpiscopal.\nMR. CHARLES T. FISHER JR., 51, R. C.\nMr. Coleman\u2014\u201cHEA\u00dfT ATTACK\" spent several\ndays in Grace Hospital, last October.\"\nMr. Fisher\u2014\u201cill for several months with lung cancer\nhad treatment at the Memorial Center for CANCER and\nAllied Diseases in New York. (Detroit Times, 4/14)\n(See COLEMAN, FISHER, Page 11)\nI'D AS SOON GO INTO BATTLE WITHOUT\nARTILLERY AS WITHOUT MY CHAPLAIN'!\n\u2014Great Britain's Gen. Montgomery, at per Paul Har\nvey, via WGN, 1:00 P.M., 3/6/51.\nBRITISH ADMIRAL'S MARVELOUS CURE 1\nSIR CECIL HARCOURT OF LONDON, ENGLAND,\nTESTIFIES TO 30 YEARS ACTIVE SERVICE IN TWO\nWORLD WARS !\u2014THANKS TO INCOMPARABLE,\nIMPERATIVE CHRIST SCIENCE, UNIVERSAL MESSIAH\nHEALING, AFTER BEING MEDICALLY INVALIDED\nOUT OF SERVCE!\nSee C. S. Sentinel, April 19, \"Radio Program No. 239,\np. 688.\" Heard Sunday, April 13, CKLW; Wed., 7:15 AM,\nApril 16, FM Radio, 103.5 Meg.\n'ALL SATAN'S APPLES HAVE WORMS' l\nat per Dr. Rice of Chicago, Temple Baptist Church,\nTV, Sat. night, 4/12.\n\nSunday., 4/13\u2014NBC-TV, 11:00 A.M.,\nTHE VERY REVEREND DEAN JAMES PIKE:\n'GOD TOOK THE RISK OF GIVING US FREEDOM.\nYOU CAN SHAKE YOUR FIST AT HIM\nTHROUGHOUT ETERNITY' I\nCOD VIA HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nWHAT PATHETIC, INFANTILE THEOLOGY FROM\nA NEWLY ELECTED BISHOpt\nAND YET, BISHOP DEAN PIKE IS A GRAND,\nPROTESTANT LEADER, BUT HE IS SOMETHING\n(Sm APPLES HAVE WORMS, Pag* 11)\nTHE DEVIL'S RIUTHER'S AUTO RECESSION I\nGOD VIA HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nDEVIL'S STEEL STRIKE THE 'WARM4IP' I\nIN CLEVELAND LAST YEAR,\nREUTHER FIRES HITLER-GOEBBELS LIKE BLAST\nCONFIDENCE-DESTROYING BOMB I\nSPIRITUAL LUNACY OF COVETOUSNESS\nAND STEALING. WITHIN THE L A W, ENACTED\nBY THE DEVIL'S DEMOCRATS AND THE \"SATAN\nBOUND\" SUPREME COURT OF THE '3o's 111\n4 DAYS WORK, 5 DAYS PAY. AND INCREASED\nFRINGE BENEFITS DEMANDED I\nIF YOU CANNOT ACHIEVE AN HONEST\nSUCCESS, STEAL IT FROM THE EMPLOYERS\nAND THE PUBLIC I\nA TIP OFF\u2014\nREUTHER'S VOICE-THE DEVIL SOUNDING OFF I\nPART 2\n\"BY THEIR FRUITS YE SHALL KNOW THEM\"\n\u2014Christ Jesut.\nF. D. R. AND THE DEVIL'S DEMOCRATS FORM\nALLIANCES WITH THE UNDERWORLDS OF U. S. AND\nRUSSIA,\nNINE TO TEN MILLION UNEMPLOYED!, 1940.\nTHE DEMOCRATIC INFAMY AND SPIRITUAL LUNACY\nPERMITS THE PEARL HARBOR 100 BILLION\nCATASTROPHE, WITH SUBSEQUENT LOSS OF CHINA\nTO THE 'REDS,' AND THE UNDERMINING OF THE\n'FREE NATIONS'' PRESTIGE, POWER, AND CHRISTIAN\nBUILDUP IN THE FAR EAST AND THAT ISN'T\nTHE HALF OF IT\nPRESENT UNEMPLOYMENT THE UNSUCCESSFUL\nEFFORTS TO STEAL CONTROL OF AMERICAN\nINDUSTRY\n\n(See REUTHER'S AUTO RECESSION, Page 11)\nMICHIGAN 'NEIGHBOR THEME' BUCKS\nRECESSION\nBy Godfrey Sperling, Jr.\n(C. S. Monitor, 4/2)\nSTURGIS, Mich.\u2014When one finds a little city of 10,600\nplanning and initiating an elaborate program for putting\nnew vigor Into the national economy, it become*\nthat America's recession is up against a formidable adver\nsary.\nAuthor Sturgis' \u201cHelp Your Neighbor\" project it Harold\nS. Pringle, general manager of the Sturgis Journal. The\nidea stems from his desire that the country avoid the gov\nernmental devices used to fight the depression of the 1930s\n\u2014such as WPA. He feels that business and communities\nworking together can beat this recession before it really\ngets under way.\n(See NEIGHBOR THEME, Page 11)\nGUY NUNN-VOICE OF THE DEVIL'S UAW-CIO\nHUNDRED BILLION 'STEAL':\n'RIGHT-TO-WORK LAWS A FRAUD'!\nMR. NUNN: IS THAT OF THE SAME QUALITY AS\nTHAT OF THE BIG LIE OF YOU PEOPLE FOR SEVERAL\nYEARS THAT TAFT-HARTLEY IS A SLAVE\nLABOR LAW?\nYOU SAY 'RIGHT-TO-WORK LAWS' PROVIDE NO\nJOBS! OBVIOUSLY NOT\nTHEY ARE DESIGNED TO PREVENT YOU UNION\nRACKETEERS FROM BLUDGEONING, FORCING MEN\nINTO UNIONS VIA YOUR DAMNABLE GOONS I\nSUCH IS THE AMERICAN VERSION OF THE\nGERMAN GOEBBELS, MAZEY, GUNACA, AND THE REST\nOF YOUR WOULD-BE PROSTITUTES' OF THE\nAMERICAN WAY OF LIFE SPIRITUAL ADULTERERS\nOF THE CONSTITUTION OF THE U. S.\nTHIS AUTOMOBILE RECESSION CAN BE CHARAC\nTERIZED IN VARYING PHRASEOLOGY, BUT ONE\nTHAT WOULD BE VERY ACCURATE IS THIS:\nTHE DEVIL'S REUTHER'S, UAW'S RECESSION!\n(in reply to Guy Nunn't statement* of Mon., 4/14)\nANTI RECESSION INSURANCE\n\"WHAT CONGRESS CAN DO\"\n1. OUTLAW COMPULSORY UNIONISM AS\nPERMITTED IN TAFT-HARTLEY ACT.\n2. APPLY ANTI TRUST LAWS TO ALL FORMS\nOF MONOPOLY AND REPEAL ALL FEDERAL\nLAWS GIVING LABOR MONOPOLIES\nSPECIAL PRIVILEGES DENIED TO OTHERS.\"\n(Sa* ANTI RECESSION, Pag* 11)\nSTOCKS RALLY, BUSINESS PICKUP SEEN\n(Fr** Pr.it, 4/16)\nNEW YORK (UP)\u2014 Th* (lock* mark*! racovary (walled\nto nearly five billion dollar* Tuetday. Growing feeling that\nthe recettion It bottoming out and that butinest will begin\nto pick up, at well at technical factor*, contributed to the\nimprovement in the market.\nThe trading pace wet ttepped up to the beat' level In\nmore than a month. Turnover totaled 2,590,000 tharet\n\u2022gainst 2,180,000 on Monday.\nThere were good gains in virtually all groups. The\nchemicals, steels, non-ferrous metals were particulerly\nstrong.\nOs 1,134 issues treded, 646 were higher, 243 lower.\ne e\nTribune\nRepresenting \u201cOur Father-Mother Gods'* our Divine Publisher\nCrusader Tot The Invincible Triumphant Divine Right. 0 f Mae\nDETROIT, MICHIGAN, SATURDAY, APRIL 26, 1958\"\n-FEAR NO EVIL\nIZfLi Dk. MigLu W;J\nBy Elizabeth Ellington\nJesus said: \u201cBehold I give you power to tread on ser\npents and scorpions and over all the power of the enemy:\nand nothing shall by any means hurt you.\u201d (Luke 10:19)\nREPENTANCE AND RE\nDEMPTION\nChrist Josus, tho redeemer,\nthe sevior, of tho world lib\norated mankind from sin, dis\nease, end death, through tho\noneness of Mind. And wo\nshould reflect that Mind in\nour .daily lift through re\npentance.\nPaul exhorted to unity\n\u201cWITH ALL LOWLINESS,\nAND MEEKNESS, WITH\nLONG SUFFERING, FOR\nBEARING ONE ANOTHER\nIN LOVE.\u201d\n\nLISTEN FOR THE VOICE\nOF TRUTH\nFor us to put in practice\nthe good things we have\nlearned, we must become\naccustomed to listening to\nthe voice of God, and ad\nhering to divine Principle.\nOur redemption is in God\nthrough Christ.\nAt Gen. Taylor Sees It\nNATION URGED TO HAVE FAITH\nIN U. S. MIGHT\nBy Gen. Maxwell D. Taylor\nChief of Staff, United States Army\n..(Free Press, 4/15)\nWASHINGTON\u2014I should like to plead tne case for\ngreeter faith in the effectiveness of our military strength.\nI believe that many of us fail to recognize the great\ndeterrent military strength which has been developed in\nour armed forces over the years. Yet, if we are to derive\nfull benefit from this strength, it is important that we act\nin full realization of its existence in being.\n(See NATION URGED, Page 11)\nGOD'S DETROIT TRIBUNE SAYS:\nPARCEL POST AND MAIL ORDER HOUSES\nMADE HEBREW AND CHRISTIAN MILLIONAIRES!\nAND RUINED NUMEROUS SMALL BUSINESSES!\nAND TAXPAYERS FINANCED THE\nPARCEL POST 1\n\"P. 0. CALLED HYPOCRITICAL\nIN ITS PARCEL POST STAND\"\n(N.Y. Tribune)\nThe position of the Post Office Department that the par\ncel post system \"pays its own way\" is \"sheer hypocrisy\"\nand such a statement is \"incorrect and grossly misleading,\"\nA. L. Hammell, president of Railway Express Agency, said\nyesterday in comment on the department's stand on pending\nmail rate legislation.\n(See PARCEL POST, Page 11)\n\"LIGHTNER SEES THREAT OF DOLE\nNAM Head, Speaking Here, Hits\nUnion-Backed Program\"\n(Free\n\n\"LIGHTNER TIES SLUMP TO CURBS\nON BUSINESS\"\n(N*ws, 4/14)\n\n\"HE BLAMES TAXES. WAGES FOR SLUMP\"\nBy James Boynton (Det. Times, 4/15)\nThe recession has been brought about by the present\nnational tax policy and wage increases which outstrip g\u00ab' ns\nin productivity, the Economic Club of Detroit was told\nyesterday.\n(See LIGHTNER SEES THREAT, Page 11)\nNEED FOR BETTER-MADE CARS\nLetter to The Christian Science'Monitor:\nMay I add a few comments on the two sub|ects of\ndeclining sales of American-made care and large carl vs.\nsmall carat v w\nMy PRESENT IMPORTED car and Its predecessor of\nequal make and model were the first card I ever owned\nwhich were COMPLETELY FREE PROM LEAKS AND\nDRAFTS FROM THE TIME OF DELIVERY. Water leaks and\n\u2022air drafts were DEFECTS COMMON to all my previously\nowned cars, including CARS OF THE THREE LEADING\nAMERICAN MANUFACTURERS. My present AMERICAN\nMADE STATION WAGON was EXTREMELY DRAFTY and\n*t took nearly a HALF A YEAR of correspondence and\n\u2022monstratlons to induce the reluctant. manufacturer TO\n(See BETTER-MADE CARS, Pago 2)\nDETROIT\nQuoting from Mrs. Eddy\u2019s\nProse Works, \u201cNo and Yes,\u201d\nshe has stated:\n\u201cAs mortals, we need to\ndiscern tho claims of evil,\nand to fight those claims,\nnot as realities, but as illu\nsions; but Deity can have no\nsuch warfare against Himself.\n\u201cKnowledge of a man\u2019s\nphysical personality is not\nsufficient to inform us as to\nthe amount of good or evil\nhe possessed. Hence we can\nnot understand God or man\nthrough the person of either.\n\u201cGOD IS ALL-IN-ALL; but\nHe is definite and individ\nual, the omnipresent and om\nniscient Mind; and mans in\ndividuality is God\u2019s .own im\nage and likeness, \u2014even the\nimmeasurable idea of divine\nj Mind. In the Science of good,\nevil loses all place, person,\n(Continued on Peg* 4)","height":"28053","width":"18816"}}
